Title: Benchmarking alternative frameworks for microbiome data science
Description:
    This repository hosts an extensive performance benchmark between three
    major frameworks for microbiome data science (mia, phyloseq and QIIME 2).
    The benchmark includes five common operations performed in microbiome data
    analysis, for which performance is measured in terms of execution time and
    allocated memory.
